# ID allocated to the new tag
prusa3d.nfc.util.TagID.1.0 tag

# What antenna the tag has been detected on
# If tag switches antennas, the reader will emit TagLost (for the original antenna) followed by TagDetected on the new one (and with a possibly different ID)
prusa3d.nfc.util.AntennaID.1.0 antenna

@sealed
